                           OPERATION DESERT STORM

Typed by ???  Edited by PARASITE.


YOUR ORDERS:  BOMB IRAQI TARGETS

YOUR TARGETS ARE AS FOLLOWS:
     Marked Military Sites
     Marked Industrial Sites
     Mobile SCUD Missile Launchers
     SCUD Missile Stockpiles
     Enemy Soldiers
     Fuel Refineries
     All Anti-Aircraft Battery

 New laser guided bombs will ensure highest accuracy in destroying targets.

 System computer will highlight military and industrial targets with
 cross-hairs

 Intelligence reports numerous Mobile SCUD Missile Launcher decoys.  The
 visual difference between the decoys and the actual Launchers is as of
 yet unknown.

 Beware of heavy ground-fire when the air raid sirens sound.

 DO NOT bomb civilian [READ: unmarked] installations.

 DO NOT bomb oil fields.


 This game was made on the Shoot Em Up Construction Kit by Carmen Rizzolo.

 For additional effect: Crank up your contrast and lower the brightness
 slightly.  Help support our troops out there doing the REAL THING!


IRAQI JESTS...

 SCUD: Stupid Crummy Ugly Dictator

 Hussain says he's talking to God while he's living 60 feet underground.
 I have a feeling it's not God he's talking to!

 With the recent drop in oil prices, George Bush has decided to attack
 Century 21 to drop the high cost of real estate.

End.
